lead_paragraph: World number one Serena Williams opened her U.S. Open account with a tidy 6-3 6-3 win over Ekaterina Makarova on Tuesday, to join her sister Venus in the second round of the year's final grand slam.

headline.print_headline: Williams Sister Act Through to U.S. Open Second Round
